      "id": "PopularPost15475",
      "post_content": "More effective in the early to mid-game because \"half of your life\" only sounds threatening if you have a larger life total to lose half of. You'll have to figure out what to do for the extra turn because otherwise it's a waste. Your opponent might call your bluff and let you have an extra turn, which could be card advantage, but a very small one. Plan ahead for this card.",
